[{"Id": 1016994, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "It has arrived in the book Al Mukhtar min Kalemaatil Imam al-Mahdi (a): With regards to the Istekhara through chaplet, such Istekhara is permissible which narrated from Imam Mahdi (a). One of the clerics permitted me to perform this Istekhara so that I can perform it for myself and also permitted me to allow others to perform it. Therefore, with respect to the permission I was granted, in the context of explaining how to perform this Istekhara, I give permission to everyone so that they can perform Istekhara in the following way: Begin by saying…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Saaheb-e-kitaab Al-Mukhtar man kalemaatul Imam Al-Mahdi (a) farmate hai: Hamare paas tasbeeh se istekhaare ka ek aur sahih tareeqa hai jis ki sanad Hazrat Imam-e-Asr (a) tak pohonchti hai aur baaz ulma ne mujhe ijaazat di hai keh is tareeqe ke mutabiq istekhaara karo aur dusro’n ko bhi is tareeqe se anjaam dene ki ijaazat do, ham ne kuchh logo’n ko is ki ijaazat di hai, pehle kahe…", "UrduDescription": "المختار من کلمات الامام المھدی کا مصنف کہتے ہیں کہ ہم تسبیح کے ساتھ استخارہ میں ایک مجازی طریقہ رکھتے ہیں کہ جو حضرت حجت کے ساتھ متصل ہے علماء میں سے ایک نے مجھے اجازت دی ہے کہ اس طریقہ پر استخارہ انجام دوں دوسروں کو بھی اجازت دیتاہوں میں نے بھی بعض کو اس طریقہ کی اجازت دی ہے اور وہ استکارہ اس طرح ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicR